CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.tb_resultado_validacao_cruces` AS

WITH base_sheet AS (
    SELECT 
      -- Adicionei DISTINCT para evitar que duplicidade de carga (linhas identicas) 
      -- acione a Flag 6 indevidamente
      DISTINCT
      id_de_deuda_indique_a_qu_id_de_deuda_corresponde_esta_transferencia AS id_deuda,
      SAFE_CAST(REPLACE(monto_total, ',', '.') AS FLOAT64) AS monto_transferido,
      -- Garante que tipo_conta nunca seja nulo para não quebrar o LIKE depois
      IFNULL(LOWER(cul_es_el_tipo_de_cuenta), '') AS tipo_conta, 
      TRIM(cbu_22_dgitos) AS cbu_informado,
      issue_en_salesforce as issue_salesforce
    FROM
      `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.tb_carga_integridade`
  ),

  base_sheet_com_contagem AS (
    SELECT
      *,
      -- Movemos a contagem para cá, após o DISTINCT
      COUNT(*) OVER (
        PARTITION BY id_deuda, SAFE_CAST(monto_transferido AS NUMERIC)
      ) as qtd_ocorrencias
    FROM base_sheet
  ),

  base_bq AS (
    SELECT
      CAST(DEBT_ID AS INT64) AS DEBT_ID,
      DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT,
      DEBT_STATUS_DETAIL,
      DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID 
    FROM `meli-bi-data.WHOWNER.BT_MP_DISB_DEBT`
    WHERE DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID IN (442, 77, 459, 437) 
    -- DICA: Se houver risco de duplicidade no BQ, descomente a linha abaixo:
    -- QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY DEBT_ID ORDER BY DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT DESC) = 1
  ),

  JOINED_DATA AS (
    SELECT 
      sheet.id_deuda,
      sheet.monto_transferido,
      bq.DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT,
      sheet.cbu_informado,
      sheet.issue_salesforce,
      sheet.tipo_conta,
      sheet.qtd_ocorrencias,         
      bq.DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID,
      bq.DEBT_STATUS_DETAIL,
      bq.DEBT_ID AS bq_id_check
    FROM base_sheet_com_contagem sheet
    LEFT JOIN base_bq bq ON CAST(sheet.id_deuda as STRING) = CAST(bq.DEBT_ID AS STRING)
  ),

  CALC_FLAGS AS (
    SELECT 
      *,
      CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() as data_execucao,
      (IFNULL(monto_transferido, 0) - IFNULL(DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT, 0)) as diferenca,

      -- ======================================================================
      -- DEFINIÇÃO DAS FLAGS (BLINDAGEM CONTRA NULL)
      -- Usamos COALESCE(..., FALSE) para garantir booleano puro
      -- ======================================================================

      -- CRUCE 2: ID inexistente
      COALESCE(bq_id_check IS NULL, FALSE) AS flag_cruce_2_id_inexistente,

      -- DATA SUJA: Valor nulo
      COALESCE(monto_transferido IS NULL, FALSE) AS flag_data_suja,

      -- CRUCE 6: Duplicidade (Agora baseada na contagem pós-distinct)
      COALESCE(qtd_ocorrencias > 1, FALSE) AS flag_cruce_6_duplicado,

      -- CRUCE 5: CBU Inválido
      COALESCE(cbu_informado IS NOT NULL AND NOT REGEXP_CONTAINS(cbu_informado, r'^[0-9]{22}$'), FALSE) AS flag_cruce_5_cbu_invalido,

      -- CRUCE 7: Tipo de Dívida Incorreto
      -- Como usamos IFNULL no tipo_conta lá em cima, o LIKE não vai retornar NULL
      COALESCE(bq_id_check IS NOT NULL AND (
          (tipo_conta LIKE '%no remun%' AND DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID NOT IN (77, 437, 459))
          OR
          (tipo_conta NOT LIKE '%no remun%' AND tipo_conta LIKE '%remun%' AND DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID != 442)
      ), FALSE) AS flag_cruce_7_debt_type,

      -- CRUCE 1: Valor Planilha > Banco
      COALESCE(bq_id_check IS NOT NULL AND monto_transferido IS NOT NULL AND TRUNC(monto_transferido) > TRUNC(DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT), FALSE) AS flag_cruce_1_valor_maior,

      -- CRUCE 4: Valor Planilha < Banco
      COALESCE(bq_id_check IS NOT NULL AND monto_transferido IS NOT NULL AND TRUNC(monto_transferido) < TRUNC(DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT), FALSE) AS flag_cruce_4_valor_menor,

      -- CRUCE 3: Status inválido
      COALESCE(bq_id_check IS NOT NULL 
       AND (tipo_conta LIKE '%remun%') 
       AND (DEBT_STATUS_DETAIL NOT IN ('executed', 'partially_executed','awaiting_confirmation')) 
       AND (DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID = 442), FALSE
      ) AS flag_cruce_3_status_invalido

    FROM JOINED_DATA
  )

SELECT 
  id_deuda,
  data_execucao,
  monto_transferido,
  DEBT_PAID_AMOUNT,
  diferenca,
  cbu_informado,
  issue_salesforce,
  tipo_conta,
  DEBT_DEBT_TYPE_ID,

  flag_cruce_1_valor_maior,
  flag_cruce_2_id_inexistente,
  flag_cruce_3_status_invalido,
  flag_cruce_4_valor_menor,
  flag_cruce_5_cbu_invalido,
  flag_cruce_6_duplicado,
  flag_cruce_7_debt_type,
  flag_data_suja,

  CASE 
    WHEN flag_cruce_1_valor_maior OR flag_cruce_2_id_inexistente OR flag_cruce_3_status_invalido OR 
         flag_cruce_4_valor_menor OR flag_cruce_5_cbu_invalido OR flag_cruce_6_duplicado OR 
         flag_cruce_7_debt_type OR flag_data_suja 
    THEN 'COM_ERRO'
    ELSE 'OK'
  END AS status_geral

FROM CALC_FLAGS

CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `ddme000426-gopr4nla6zo-furyid.STG.tb_carga_integridade` (
  carimbo_de_datahora STRING,
  endereco_de_email STRING,
  fecha_de_solicitud_de_transferencia STRING,
  issue_en_salesforce STRING,
  n_de_expediente STRING,
  cartula_de_la_causa STRING,
  monto_total STRING,
  id_de_deuda_indique_a_qu_id_de_deuda_corresponde_esta_transferencia STRING,
  cul_es_el_tipo_de_cuenta STRING,
  cbu_22_dgitos STRING,
  banco_de_destino STRING,
  cuit_del_banco_que_recibe STRING,
  n_de_cuenta STRING,
  sociedad STRING,
  transferido_remunerado STRING,
  transferido_no_remunerado STRING,
  issue_monto STRING,
  enviado_a_finanzas STRING
);
